ualTo(Right(List(5, 4, 7)))\n    assertThat(document.hcursor.get[String](\"summary\")).isEqualTo(Right(\"alpha:3\"))\n  }\n\n  @Test\n  def buildsTopLevelScalarLiteralsAndInterpolatedValues(): Unit = {\n"}]}
